permafrost.tundra.server.invoke

Class RetryableServiceProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • permafrost.tundra.server.invoke.AbstractInvokeChainProcessor
      • permafrost.tundra.server.invoke.RetryableServiceProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.wm.app.b2b.server.invoke.InvokeChainProcessor, Startable

    public class RetryableServiceProcessor
extends AbstractInvokeChainProcessor
    Converts any exceptions thrown by a registered service invocation to be instances of ISRuntimeException to support being retried.
